HEADWORD: Negotiator
<hw>Ne*go"ti*a`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>n⟦eacute⟧gociateur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who negotiates; a person
